            <strong>Nutrient Groups:</strong> Fast Protein + Fast Carbs/High GI
            Carbs<br /><br />
            <strong>What to Eat:</strong><br /><br />
            <strong>Vegetarians:</strong> Whey protein shake and Dextrose
