            <strong>Non-Vegetarians:</strong> Whey protein shake and Dextrose
            Monohydrate <br /><strong>Calories:</strong> 190, Fat: 13g, Carbs:
            25g, Fiber: 3g, Protein: 4g
          </p>
          <h3>Meal 7: Dinner</h3>
